name: Smoke
description: Without any clear goal, fooling around with parameters while looking to the first two seasons of Mad Men. God they smoke! So I forgot color. This digital fog is 100% white, black and gray men swirling around. Pixel based figures fighting pixelation, doing their best to imitate nature.  2012 CR 709 https://hansup.be/2012_smoke-01_animation_hans-verhaegen.html
